&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;: Work closely with Product, R&amp;amp;D, and Security teams to address customer feedback and ensure solutions align with Fireblocks’ capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Domain Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;: Stay informed about trends and challenges in the blockchain, digital assets, and evolving use cases (e.g., custody, tokenization, payments, DeFi), positioning Fireblocks as a trusted technical advisor.&lt;/li&gt;
