&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in &lt;strong&gt;crypto, fintech, or highly regulated financial environments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with the NIST Cybersecurity Framework (CSF) 2.0, Cloud Security Alliance (CSA) controls matrix, offensive security frameworks (MITRE), etc.&lt;/li&gt;
