&lt;p&gt;Connecting exchanges, OTC desks, custodians, and wallets, the Fireblocks Network settles trillions in crypto trading volume, and delivers a seamless trading experience by reducing friction, unlocking capital efficiency and mitigating counterparty risk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Liquidity Team is dedicated to developing Fireblocks&#39; trading solutions. Delivering a reliable, seamless, fast, and secure trading experience for users in both crypto and fiat assets.&lt;/p&gt;
